<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <%- include("../fragmente/head.ejs"); %>

  <body style="overflow-x: hidden">
    <%- include("../fragmente/header.ejs"); %> <%-
    include("../fragmente/fixed-elements.ejs"); %>
    <div style="margin-left: 40px; margin-right: 40px"">
      <div>
        <h2 style="font-size: 25px; margin: 10px; margin-left: 0px">
          Despre Noi
        </h2>
        Bine ați venit la Pet Paradise, locul unde iubirea pentru animale și
        grija pentru bunăstarea lor se împletesc armonios! Suntem o echipă de
        profesioniști dedicați, pasionați de tot ceea ce înseamnă îngrijirea și
        fericirea prietenilor noștri necuvântători.
        <h2 style="font-size: 25px; margin: 10px; margin-left: 0px">
          Cine Suntem?
        </h2>
        Pet Paradise este mai mult decât un simplu magazin pentru animale de
        companie. Suntem o familie unită de dragostea pentru animale și dorința
        de a le oferi cele mai bune condiții de viață. Cu o experiență de peste
        10 ani în domeniu, ne-am dedicat să aducem pe piață produse de calitate
        superioară și servicii excepționale pentru animalele voastre de
        companie.
      </div>

      <video
        style="margin-top: 40px; width: 30%; max-width: 500px; min-width: 300px"
        controls
        poster="resurse/images/cat.jpg"
        src="resurse/videos/dogs.mp4"
      >
        <track
          src="resurse/videos/captions-dogs-en.vtt"
          kind="captions"
          srclang="en"
          label="English"
        />
        <track
          src="resurse/videos/captions-dogs.vtt"
          kind="captions"
          srclang="ro"
          label="Romanian"
          default
        />
      </video>
    </div>
  <h1 style="text-align: center;">FAQ</h1>
    <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample" style="margin:10vw;margin-top:40px">
      <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample" style="margin:10vw;margin-top:40px">
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
            <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
              What types of pets do you sell?
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <strong>We offer a variety of pets including:</strong>
              <ul>
                <li>Dogs</li>
                <li>Cats</li>
                <li>Birds</li>
                <li>Fish</li>
                <li>Small mammals (hamsters, rabbits, etc.)</li>
                <li>Reptiles</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
              What are your store hours?
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <strong>Our store hours are:</strong>
              <ul>
                <li>Monday to Friday: 9 AM - 8 PM</li>
                <li>Saturday: 10 AM - 6 PM</li>
                <li>Sunday: 11 AM - 5 PM</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
              Do you offer pet grooming services?
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <strong>Yes, we offer a range of pet grooming services including:</strong>
              <ul>
                <li>Bathing</li>
                <li>Haircuts</li>
                <li>Nail trimming</li>
                <li>Ear cleaning</li>
                <li>Teeth brushing</li>
              </ul>
              Please contact us to schedule an appointment.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
              Do you provide veterinary services?
            </button>
          </h2>
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <strong>Yes, we have an in-store veterinary clinic offering services such as:</strong>
              <ul>
                <li>Routine check-ups</li>
                <li>Vaccinations</li>
                <li>Microchipping</li>
                <li>Spaying and neutering</li>
                <li>Dental care</li>
              </ul>
              Please call us to book an appointment with our veterinarian.
            </div>
          </div>
          </div>
    </div>  
    
    <%- include("../fragmente/footer.ejs"); %> <%-
    include("../fragmente/scripts.ejs"); %>
  </body>
</html>
